00:42:54,030 --> 00:42:55,030
Let's go play over there,

844
00:42:55,030 --> 00:42:55,830
shall we?

845
00:42:56,000 --> 00:42:56,760
I...

846
00:42:56,760 --> 00:42:57,190
Guihong.

847
00:42:57,190 --> 00:42:59,070
Have found a really fun place.

848
00:42:59,350 --> 00:42:59,980
Father.

849
00:43:04,180 --> 00:43:06,540
[Empress Chu Yurong]

850
00:43:07,150 --> 00:43:08,110
Let me carry you.

851
00:43:10,320 --> 00:43:11,370
Let's go.

852
00:43:25,550 --> 00:43:26,800
Heng, when we return to the palace today,

853
00:43:26,800 --> 00:43:28,880
ride in my carriage.

854
00:43:37,800 --> 00:43:38,590
Come.

855
00:43:42,240 --> 00:43:42,950
Come.

856
00:43:47,770 --> 00:43:48,840
What are you doing?

857
00:43:50,790 --> 00:43:52,480
That's the right expression.

858
00:43:53,760 --> 00:43:55,560
When I was your age,

859
00:43:55,710 --> 00:43:57,630
I would constantly
pester my father and brother

860
00:43:57,630 --> 00:43:59,050
to go horse racing and hunting,

861
00:43:59,050 --> 00:44:00,510
having the time of my life.

862
00:44:01,060 --> 00:44:02,950
If you carry too many worries,

863
00:44:03,000 --> 00:44:04,410
you'll age quickly,

864
00:44:04,770 --> 00:44:05,900
and once you're old,

865
00:44:07,120 --> 00:44:09,780
you can never return to your youth.

866
00:44:13,560 --> 00:44:15,010
His Majesty is

867
00:44:15,480 --> 00:44:18,050
still so childish despite his age.

868
00:44:18,780 --> 00:44:20,330
He's not ignoring you

869
00:44:20,460 --> 00:44:23,260
because he's just
competing with Chancellor Gao.

870
00:44:25,100 --> 00:44:25,910
Eat up.

871
00:44:27,080 --> 00:44:28,170
When you're done,

872
00:44:28,760 --> 00:44:30,280
I'll take you hunting for

873
00:44:30,280 --> 00:44:31,540
an even bigger rabbit.

874
00:44:31,820 --> 00:44:33,210
We can make

875
00:44:33,240 --> 00:44:35,700
a warm scarf
for your mother, how about that?

876
00:45:14,840 --> 00:45:16,590
This path doesn't lead to the palace.

877
00:45:16,590 --> 00:45:18,220
Mother brought me here

878
00:45:18,550 --> 00:45:20,070
to catch rabbits.

879
00:45:20,110 --> 00:45:21,030
You're lying!

880
00:45:25,230 --> 00:45:26,400
Are you going to eat or not?

881
00:45:25,730 --> 00:45:28,370
[Cold Palace]

882
00:45:26,440 --> 00:45:27,670
If not, you'll starve.

883
00:45:27,670 --> 00:45:28,480
Come out.

884
00:45:28,690 --> 00:45:29,480
Leave us.

885
00:45:30,480 --> 00:45:31,280
Yes.

886
00:45:31,710 --> 00:45:32,510
Open the door.

887
00:45:34,680 --> 00:45:36,410
Where are the things I gave you?

888
00:45:37,070 --> 00:45:38,200
Give them back to me.

889
00:45:41,320 --> 00:45:42,180
Give them back!

890
00:45:43,840 --> 00:45:44,640
I burned them.

891
00:46:01,590 --> 00:46:02,280
Wait.

892
00:46:05,760 --> 00:46:07,520
I didn't kill your aunt,

893
00:46:08,730 --> 00:46:09,730
do you believe me?

894
00:46:17,030 --> 00:46:18,890
So you and Chu Guihong

895
00:46:19,000 --> 00:46:20,710
have such a history together,

896
00:46:23,760 --> 00:46:25,280
how fascinating.

897
00:46:29,450 --> 00:46:32,740
Those who abandon me and disturb my heart

898
00:46:34,190 --> 00:46:35,250
are all obstacles,

899
00:46:37,820 --> 00:46:39,070
not to be longed for.

900
00:46:40,880 --> 00:46:41,680
Didn't you two

901
00:46:42,280 --> 00:46:44,000
just reconcile?

902
00:46:47,710 --> 00:46:49,070
What reconciliation?

903
00:46:50,320 --> 00:46:52,310
Even if we patch things up temporarily,

904
00:46:52,310 --> 00:46:54,110
we'll end up as strangers again.

905
00:46:55,030 --> 00:46:56,690
Besides, the one on the throne

906
00:46:57,150 --> 00:46:59,230
constantly reminds me:

907
00:46:59,880 --> 00:47:02,360
when two tigers fight, one must perish.

908
00:47:03,510 --> 00:47:04,590
If I don't win,

909
00:47:06,510 --> 00:47:07,920
then I can only die.

